    "False decisions in automated diagnosis may have very harmful results [141].",
    "Moreover, some studies have found that ML algorithms are prone to misinterpreting unpleasant disgust as pain in facial expressions [141].The Complex Nature of Pain Automatic pain detection is challenging because it is complex, subjective, and subject to a variety of factors, such as personal and socialcultural perspectives, as well as past experiences of pain [143].",
    "Several studies worldwide are engaged in the field of automatic pain assessments, but the lack of adequate knowledge can represent an obstacle to the potential translation into clinical practice.",
